<!DOCTYPE html>
<html class="sub">
<head>
  <% include ../partials/header.ejs %>
  <div class="sub designcustom" itemscope itemtype = "http://schema.org/WebPage" role="main">
    <% include ../partials/nav.ejs %>
    <div class="container" itemscope = "" itemtype = "http://schema.org/CreativeWork">
      <section>
        <form method="post" action="/mypage/submit" onSubmit="CheckFormInput();">
          <fieldset>
            <legend>
              <h2 class="section_title left">
                <strong>기본 인적사항</strong>
                <span>기본적으로 사용되는 회원정보입니다.</span>
              </h2>
            </legend>
            <ul class="col-xs-12">
              <li class="clearfix">
                <h3 class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-2">
                  <label for="joinId">아이디</label>
                </h3>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-10">
                  <input id="joinId" name="id" type="text" value="<%= id %>" aria-required="true" aria-readonly="true" readonly required />
                  <input type="hidden" id="joinCheckId" value="yes">
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="clearfix">
                <h3 class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-2">
                  <label for="joinPassword">비밀번호</label>
                </h3>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-10">
                  <input id="joinPassword" name="pw" type="password" data-toggle="tooltip" placeholder="비밀번호를 입력하세요 (숫자,알파벳만 입력 가능합니다. 10자 이상)" aria-required="true" required />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="clearfix">
                <h3 class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-2">
                  <label for="joinNickname">닉네임</label>
                </h3>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-10">
                  <input id="joinNickname" name="nickname" type="text" aria-required="true" value="<%= nickname %>" data-toggle="tooltip" placeholder="닉네임을 입력하세요 (2~20자)" required />
                  <button type="button" id="joinCheckNickname" class="linebutton small dobule_check" data-item="joinNickname" value="yes" role="alert">
                    중복확인하기
                  </button>
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="clearfix">
                <h3 class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-2">
                  <label for="joinEmail">이메일</label>
                </h3>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-10">
                  <input id="joinEmail" name="email" type="text" value="<%= email %>" data-toggle="tooltip" placeholder="이메일을 입력하세요" aria-required="true" required />
                </div>
              </li>
              <li class="clearfix">
                <h3 class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-2">
                  <label for="joinTel">전화번호</label>
                </h3>
                <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-10">
                  <input id="joinTel" name="tel" type="text" value="<%= tel %>" data-toggle="tooltip" placeholder="전화번호를 입력하세요" aria-required="true" required />
                </div>
              </li>
            </ul>
            </fieldset>
            <fieldset>
              <legend>
                <h2 class="section_title left">
                  <strong>신체정보</strong>
                  <span>차후 다이어트 관련 서비스 제안시 사용될 내용입니다.</span>
                </h2>
              </legend>
              <ul class="col-xs-12">
                <li class="clearfix">
                  <h3 class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-2">
                    <label for="joinSex">성별</label>
                  </h3>
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-10">
                    <select id="joinSex" data-sex="<%= sex %>" name="sex" aria-required="true" required >
                      <option value="female">여성</option>
                      <option value="male">남성</option>
                    </select>
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="clearfix">
                  <h3 class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-2">
                    <label for="joinHeight">키</label>
                  </h3>
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-10">
                    <input id="joinHeight" name="height" type="text" value="<%= height %>" data-toggle="tooltip" placeholder="키를 입력해주세요 (숫자만 가능합니다)" aria-required="true" required />
                  </div>
                </li>
                <li class="clearfix">
                  <h3 class="col-xs-12 col-sm-12 col-md-3 col-lg-2">
                    <label for="joinWeight">몸무게</label>
                  </h3>
                  <div class="col-xs-12 col-md-9 col-lg-10">
                    <input id="joinWeight" name="weight" type="text" value="<%= weight %>" data-toggle="tooltip" placeholder="몸무게를 입력해주세요 (숫자만 가능합니다)" aria-required="true" required />
                  </div>
                </li>
              </ul>
            </fieldset>
            <div class="buttonbox">
              <button type="submit" class="linebutton middle" accesskey="s">정보변경하기</button>
            </div>
          </form>
      </section>
    </div>
  </div>
  <% include ../partials/footer.ejs %>
</body>
</html>
